description: 'Gipsy Kings' the Album, was released in the United States in 1989 and spent 40 weeks on the U.S. charts.  Gipsy Kings are a group of flamenco and pop musicians from Arles and Montpellier in the south of France, who perform in a mixture of  mostly  Spanish, but also mixing southern French dialects.
name: Gypsy Kings | Greatest Hits
